1842333 1The Academic Council shall be the principal academic body of the University and shall, subject to the provisions of this Act, the Statutes and the Ordinances, co- ordinate and exercise general supervision over the academic po icies of the University.
357026 2The constitution of the Academic Council, the term of office of its members and its powers and functions shall be prescribed by the Statutes.
